member.example:
Using built-in retry:

services.AddOpenCodeClient()
    .ConfigureRetry(retry =>
    {
        retry.MaxRetryAttempts = 5;
        retry.RetryDelaySeconds = 3;
    });


Using Polly (requires Microsoft.Extensions.Http.Polly):

services.AddOpenCodeClient()
    .AddPolicyHandler(Policy.Handle<HttpRequestException>()
        .WaitAndRetryAsync(3, i => TimeSpan.FromSeconds(Math.Pow(2, i))));

example.code:
services.AddOpenCodeClient(options =>
{
    options.BaseUrl = "http://localhost:9000";
    options.MessageTimeout = TimeSpan.FromMinutes(10);
})
.AddPolicyHandler(myRetryPolicy); // Optional Polly integration

member.example:
Basic usage:

await using var client = new OpenCodeClient();
var session = await client.CreateSessionAsync();
var response = await client.SendMessageAsync(session.Id, "Hello, OpenCode!");

example.code:
await using var scope = await client.CreateSessionScopeAsync();
// Use scope.Session...
// Session is automatically deleted when scope is disposed

member.example:
Basic usage:

await using var client = new OpenCodeClient();
var session = await client.CreateSessionAsync();
var response = await client.SendMessageAsync(session.Id, "Hello, OpenCode!");
Console.WriteLine(response.Parts.OfType<TextPart>().First().Text);
